%% Diagram: Module Federation runtime — host loads remote with shared singleton negotiation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant Host as Host App (shell)
    participant Remote as remoteEntry.js
    participant Share as Shared Scope
    participant CDN as CDN / Origin

    U->>Host: Navigate to /catalog
    Host->>CDN: GET catalog/remoteEntry.js
    CDN-->>Host: Container manifest
    Host->>Remote: init(sharedScope)
    Remote->>Share: Register react@18.2 (singleton)
    Host->>Share: Already has react@18.3 (singleton)
    Share-->>Remote: Higher semver wins · use 18.3
    Remote-->>Host: Module factory for ./ProductList
    Host->>Host: React.lazy(() => import("catalog/ProductList"))
    Host-->>U: Render with shared React instance
